  "description": "A majestic view of Yosemite Valley, featuring Yosemite Falls cascading down a sheer granite cliff face. The falls are a brilliant white streak against the dark gray and brown rock of El Capitan and Half Dome in the background. Lush green meadows extend into the foreground, dotted with trees and wildflowers. The trees frame the view and add depth, contrasting the smooth grassy fields with the rugged mountain peak. The sky is overcast with patches of clouds.",
